<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Tutorials - Trashcore System</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
  <style>
    body {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f0c29, #302b63, #24243e);
      color: #f0f0f0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: flex-start; /* Align content to top */
    }

    h1 {
      color: #bb86fc;
      margin: 1rem 0 2rem 0; /* Add top margin */
      text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(187, 134, 252, 0.4);
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      text-align: center; /* Center heading */
      width: 100%; /* Full width for centering */
    }

    .container {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center; /* Center cards */
        gap: 1.5rem; /* Space between cards */
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 500px; /* Limit max width */
        margin-top: 1rem; /* Space below heading */
    }

    .card {
      background: rgba(30, 30, 46, 0.9);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 1.8rem 1.5rem;
      width: 100%;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4),
                  0 0 20px rgba(187, 134, 252, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid #444;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
      text-align: center; /* Center content inside card */
    }

    .card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5),
                    0 0 30px rgba(187, 134, 252, 0.2);
    }

    .card h2 {
      color: #03dac6;
      margin: 0 0 1rem 0; /* Remove top margin, keep bottom */
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
    }

    .card p {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #e0e0e0;
      margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0; /* Remove top margin, add bottom */
      line-height: 1.5;
      padding: 0 0.5rem;
    }

    .cta {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #6a11cb, #2575fc);
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      width: 100%; /* Full width button */
      max-width: 250px; /* Limit width */
      font-size: 1rem;
      text-align: center; /* Ensure text is centered */
    }

    .cta:hover {
      transform: scale(1.03);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #7a1bdb, #3585ff);
    }

    /* Media Query for larger screens */
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        body {
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            margin: 1.5rem 0 2.5rem 0;
        }
        .container {
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
        }
        .card {
            padding: 2.2rem 2rem;
            width: 450px; /* Fixed width for larger screens */
        }
        .card h2 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }
        .card p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            padding: 0;
            margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
        }
        .cta {
            width: auto; /* Auto width for larger screens */
        }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Tutorials</h1>

  <div class="container">
      <div class="card">
          <h2>üöÄ Deploy Trashcore Ultra</h2>
          <p>Learn how to deploy the advanced Trashcore Ultra system on various hosting panels.</p>
          <a href="#" class="cta">View Tutorial</a> <!-- Placeholder link -->
      </div>

      <div class="card">
          <h2>‚öôÔ∏è Deploy Trashcore System</h2>
          <p>Step-by-step guide to deploying the core Trashcore System on your preferred panel.</p>
          <a href="#" class="cta">View Tutorial</a> <!-- Placeholder link -->
      </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
